  <rdf:Description rdf:about="http://publications.europa.eu/resource/pegase/199107.409275">
    <j.0:comment xml:lang="en">The Commission cannot accept the amendments relating to delegated acts - Article 290 TFEU - and Comitology issues (Recital 12; Articles 21, 22(3), 23, 33(2), and 35). The Commission can accept the amendments introduced by the Parliament in recital 5.</j.0:comment>
